name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
Framing of NEP 2020 will be remembered as a shining example of participative governance. I thank all those who have worked hard in the formulation of the NEP 2020. 

May education brighten our nation and lead it to prosperity.
translate:
Framing of NEP 2020 will be remembered as a shining example of participative governance. I thank all those who have worked hard in the formulation of the NEP 2020. 

May education brighten our nation and lead it to prosperity.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet: Aspects such as widening the availability of scholarships, strengthening infrastructure for Open and Distance Learning, Online Education and increasing the usage of technology have received great attention in the NEP. These are vital reforms for the education sector.
translate: Aspects such as widening the availability of scholarships, strengthening infrastructure for Open and Distance Learning, Online Education and increasing the usage of technology have received great attention in the NEP. These are vital reforms for the education sector.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
Respecting the spirit ‘Ek Bharat Shreshtha Bharat’, the NEP 2020 includes systems to promote Indian languages, including Sanskrit. Many foreign languages will also be offered at the secondary level. 

Indian Sign Language (ISL) will be standardised across the country.
translate:
Respecting the spirit ‘Ek Bharat Shreshtha Bharat’, the NEP 2020 includes systems to promote Indian languages, including Sanskrit. Many foreign languages will also be offered at the secondary level. 

Indian Sign Language (ISL) will be standardised across the country.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet: UG education would also include multiple entry and exit points with appropriate certification. An Academic Bank of Credit will be set up to enable digital storage of credits earned from different HEIs, which can also be transferred and counted as a part of the final degree.
translate: UG education would also include multiple entry and exit points with appropriate certification. An Academic Bank of Credit will be set up to enable digital storage of credits earned from different HEIs, which can also be transferred and counted as a part of the final degree.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet: Thanks to NEP 2020, the Indian Higher Education sector will have a holistic and multi-disciplinary approach. UG education will offer flexible curricula, creative combinations of subjects, integration of vocational education.
translate: Thanks to NEP 2020, the Indian Higher Education sector will have a holistic and multi-disciplinary approach. UG education will offer flexible curricula, creative combinations of subjects, integration of vocational education.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet: NEP 2020 has provisions to set up a Gender Inclusion Fund and also Special Education Zones. These will specially focus on making education more inclusive. NEP 2020 would improve the education infrastructure and opportunities for persons with disabilities.
translate: NEP 2020 has provisions to set up a Gender Inclusion Fund and also Special Education Zones. These will specially focus on making education more inclusive. NEP 2020 would improve the education infrastructure and opportunities for persons with disabilities.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet: Replacing 10+2 structure of school curricula with a 5+3+3+4 curricular structure will benefit the younger children. It will also be in tune with global best practices for development of mental faculties of a child. There are reforms in school curricula and pedagogy too.
translate: Replacing 10+2 structure of school curricula with a 5+3+3+4 curricular structure will benefit the younger children. It will also be in tune with global best practices for development of mental faculties of a child. There are reforms in school curricula and pedagogy too.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet: NEP 2020 gives utmost importance towards ensuring universal access to school education. There is emphasis on aspects such as better infrastructure, innovative education centres to bring back dropouts into the mainstream, facilitating multiple pathways to learning among others.
translate: NEP 2020 gives utmost importance towards ensuring universal access to school education. There is emphasis on aspects such as better infrastructure, innovative education centres to bring back dropouts into the mainstream, facilitating multiple pathways to learning among others.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
NEP 2020 is based on the pillars of:

Access.

Equity.

Quality. 

Affordability.

Accountability.

In this era of knowledge, where learning, research and innovation are important, the NEP will transform India into a vibrant knowledge hub.
translate:
NEP 2020 is based on the pillars of:

Access.

Equity.

Quality. 

Affordability.

Accountability.

In this era of knowledge, where learning, research and innovation are important, the NEP will transform India into a vibrant knowledge hub.

tweet:
आत्मनिर्भरता सही मायने में तभी संभव है, जब हमारे भीतर आत्मविश्वास हो।

Self-reliance is truly possible only when there is confidence in us.

Confidence comes only when the whole country, the whole system supports every countryman.

This is what India is doing in the midst of the conditions created by the Corona crisis, this is the government that is trying to build confidence. pic.twitter.com/eI2fIWABOw

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
सोलर पावर की ताकत का हम तब तक पूरी तरह से उपयोग नहीं कर पाएंगे, जब तक हमारे पास देश में ही बेहतर सोलर पैनल, बैटरी, उत्तम क्वालिटी की स्टोरेज कैपेसिटी ना हो।

आत्मनिर्भर भारत अभियान के तहत अब देश का लक्ष्य है कि सोलर पैनल्स सहित तमाम उपकरणों के लिए आयात पर निर्भरता खत्म करें। pic.twitter.com/2mbRYhCBzG

We will not be able to fully utilize the power of solar power unless we have better solar panels, batteries, and better quality storage capacity in the country.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
सेवा करने वाला सेवा का फल नहीं मांगता, दिन-रात निःस्वार्थ भाव से सेवा करता है।

दूसरों की निःस्वार्थ सेवा के हमारे यही संस्कार हैं, जो इस मुश्किल समय में देशवासियों के काम आ रहे हैं। pic.twitter.com/2JV22ao4D7

The one who does service does not ask for the fruits of service, does selfless service day and night.

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
उत्तर प्रदेश ने न सिर्फ संक्रमण की गति को काबू में किया हुआ है, बल्कि जिन्हें कोरोना हुआ है, वे भी तेजी से ठीक हो रहे हैं।

इसकी बहुत बड़ी वजह आप सभी लोग हैं। आप जैसे सामाजिक, धार्मिक और परोपकारी संगठनों के सेवाभाव, संकल्प और संस्कार हैं, जिनसे इस कठिन समय में बहुत मदद मिली है। pic.twitter.com/jT4MrkixY1
translate:
Uttar Pradesh has not only controlled the pace of infection, but those who have corona are also recovering fast.

The reason behind this is you all. The service, resolve and values ​​of social, religious and philanthropic organizations like you have helped a lot in this difficult time. pic.twitter.com/jT4MrkixY1

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
हमारी काशी में बाबा विश्वनाथ और मां अन्नपूर्णा दोनों विराजते हैं।

तमाम संगठनों के लिए, हम सभी के लिए यह बहुत सौभाग्य की बात है कि इस बार गरीबों की सेवा का माध्यम भगवान ने हमें बनाया।

एक तरह से आप सभी मां अन्नपूर्णा और बाबा विश्वनाथ के दूत बनकर हर जरूरतमंद तक पहुंचे। pic.twitter.com/4RS13UvqPr
translate:
Baba Vishwanath and Maa Annapurna both sit in our Kashi.

For all organizations, it is a great privilege for all of us that this time God has made us the medium of service to the poor.

In a way, all of you reached every needy by becoming the messenger of Mother Annapurna and Baba Vishwanath. pic.twitter.com/4RS13UvqPr

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
भाजपा के प्रत्येक कार्यकर्ता को अपने साथ सात ‘स’ की शक्ति लेकर आगे बढ़ना चाहिए। 
ये हैं-
पहला- सेवाभाव, 
दूसरा- संतुलन, 
तीसरा- संयम, 
चौथा- समन्वय, 
पांचवां- सकारात्मकता, 
छठा- सद्भावना 
और सातवां- संवाद। pic.twitter.com/NnelweAMV9
translate:
Every BJP worker should take the power of seven C's with him and move forward.
These are
First - service,
Second, balance
Third - moderation,
Fourth - coordination,
Fifth - positivity,
Sixth - Goodwill
And seventh- dialogue. pic.twitter.com/NnelweAMV9

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
हम चाहे कार्यकर्ता की भूमिका में हों या सरकार में, वास्तव में हम देश की और गरीबों की सेवा का माध्यम ही हैं।

यह सरकार छह सालों से इसी विचार के साथ काम कर रही है और फैसले ले रही है। pic.twitter.com/RvPG4vKdSt
translate:
Whether we are in the role of worker or in government, in reality we are the medium of service to the country and the poor.

This government has been working with this idea for six years and is taking decisions. pic.twitter.com/RvPG4vKdSt

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
कोरोना के इस संकट काल में समाज ने आपको स्नेह दिया है, विश्वास दिया है।

आप किसी गरीब की मदद कर सकें, इसके लिए समाज ने आपको साधन दिए हैं। 

यही वो स्नेह है, वो ऊर्जा है, जिसकी ताकत ने आपको थकने नहीं दिया। हमें इस ऊर्जा को और समाज की इस शक्ति को समझना चाहिए। pic.twitter.com/hB3eCnkgX7
translate:
In this crisis of Corona, the society has given you affection, faith.

The society has given you the means to help a poor person.

This is the affection, the energy, whose strength did not let you get tired. We should understand this energy and this power of society. pic.twitter.com/hB3eCnkgX7

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
हमारे लिए हमारे संगठन का मतलब है- सेवा, सबका संग, सबका साथ, सबका सुख, सबकी समृद्धि।
 
हमारा संगठन समाज हित के लिए काम करने वाला है, संघर्ष करने वाला है, समाज और देश के लिए खप जाने वाला है।
 
हमारे लिए हमेशा ‘Nation First’ रहा है। pic.twitter.com/Th2yGuef8v
translate:
For us, our organization means service, company of all, company of all, happiness of all, prosperity of all.
 
Our organization is going to work for the benefit of society, is going to struggle, it is going to be consumed for society and country.
 
'Nation First' has always been for us. pic.twitter.com/Th2yGuef8v

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
हम लोगों ने राजनीति में सत्ता को सेवा का माध्यम माना, हमने कभी भी सत्ता को अपने लाभ का माध्यम नहीं बनाया।

निःस्वार्थ सेवा ही हमारा संकल्प और संस्कार रहा है। pic.twitter.com/0OLvhZA2vy

We considered power as a medium of service in politics, we never made power our medium of profit.

Selfless service has been our resolve and values. pic.twitter.com/0OLvhZA2vy

name: Narendra Modi
tweet:
